## 画像生成AIへ渡すプロンプトの基本要素

必ず含める要素：

- Japanese infographic
- clean light background
- off-white or warm beige paper texture
- editorial infographic poster
- hand-drawn educational style
- organized layout
- readable Japanese typography
- soft accent colors
- smartphone-readable design
- no dark background
- no futuristic dark UI
- no neon cyberpunk background
- magazine-like clean composition
- generous whitespace
- clear visual hierarchy

